{"tid":801241,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"阿迪達快將接掌阿仙奴","createTime":"2018-08-31T12:55:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-31T12:57:29.000Z","uid":17641,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"566ed77473acddb85d6b127438e6f36a1a8d0181","tid":801241,"uid":17641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:55:02.000Z","msg":"阿迪達原則上已經同意接掌阿仙奴，不過雙方仍然未簽約作實。<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=kDEuW%2BW1JaXomLAtNExz5%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a5e2028e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>收到消息，阿迪達已經同意接掌阿仙奴，雖然雙方仍然未簽約作實，但估計數天內會有正式消息公布。<br />\n<br />\n阿仙奴最近辭退了一批幕後團隊，這件事也和阿迪達有關。由於阿仙奴CEO加齊迪斯很重視阿迪達，他相信這位年青教練可以幫助球隊進步。<br />\n<br />\n阿迪達預計會帶來自己的班底入主，其中辛迪卡索拉也有可能轉型為教練團，不過門將教練列文及助教保特的去向仍然未知。(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=kDEuW%2BW1JaXomLAtNExz5%2F9tTpBMMlQtk6PgfkTA9U8%3D&h=a5e2028e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"42d9c38a2ebfe87fecf8c3d4ec5c66025194c356","tid":801241,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-31T12:57:29.000Z","msg":"辛迪卡索拉仲踢緊波<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}